## **Lab-Grown Oval Cut Diamond Prices: The 2026 Arbitrage**

**Lab-grown oval cuts start at $1,790 for a 1ct E-IF — Internally Flawless, near-colorless, at 69% below the natural E-VS1 entry price of $5,720.**

The oval cut lab-grown arbitrage is one of the most compelling in the market — particularly at 2ct and 3ct sizes where natural pricing reaches $22,630–$72,790 while lab-grown offers equivalent or superior specifications at a fraction of the cost.

